name: amb
description: Propagates the observable sequence or Promise that reacts first

name: case
description: Uses selector to determine which source in sources to use

name: catch
description: Continues an observable sequence that is terminated by an exception with the next observable sequence

name: combineLatest
description: Merges the specified observable sequences into one observable sequence by using the selector function whenever any of the observable sequences produces an element

name: concat
description: Concatenates all of the specified observable sequences, as long as the previous observable sequence terminated successfully
